17oz Stoneware Avesta Mug Black - Project 62

Visit
4
(33)
Enjoy iced tea on hot sunny days or a steaming cup of joe by the evening fire in style with this 17-Ounce Stoneware Avesta Mug from Project 62 . Crafted from shiny glazed finished stoneware, this mug features a simple yet stylish look that makes it easy to mix in with the rest of your drinkware. The mug holds 17 fluid ounces — perfect for a satisfying serving of coffee, tea, cocoa or any other drink. Best of all, the stoneware mug is microwave- and dishwasher-safe for easy reheating and cleanup for added convenience. 1962 was a big year. Modernist design hit its peak and moved into homes across the country. And in Minnesota, Target was born — with the revolutionary idea to celebrate design for all. Project 62 embodies this legacy with a collection of modern pieces made for everyday living. Size: 1pc. Color: Black.
